BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:6929493@advancements.scouting.org
DTSTAMP:20260426T100711Z
CREATED:20260416T223140Z
ORGANIZER:William Mau
DTSTART:20260508T040000Z
DTEND:20260511T034500Z
SUMMARY:Lake George Camporee
DESCRIPTION:Troops will camp nearby at the Battleground Campground.  Sites will be assigned toward the end of April.  Your camporee fee already includes the campsite fee.Troops will cook their own meals (or can walk to restaurants in the village if accompanied by 2-deep leadership).Discount hotel rooms (starting at $150) available for those who so wish\, at the adjacent Fort William Henry Hotel.  Please contact us if interested.Cub Packs wishing to camp can rent a site or cabin at Camp Wakpominee\, only a 20 minute drive!  Click here to reserve:  https://campreservation.com/364/Camps/810
URL:https://advancements.scouting.org/calendar/event/6929493
LOCATION:Fort William Henry
END:VEVENT
